	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I don't know that the game you selected does the SEEPROM the same way. But if it did, you remove the MaskROM chips (or chips if there are two 8bit chips) but you leave the SEEPROM in there. Then patch the region code in mega man wily wars from E to U and it will run on a US Genesis.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


